# tests/scripts/ — fallback location for bash/python test scripts
#
# Use this folder when your project has no native test framework (pure
# container service, infra repo, glue code). Each script:
#
#   1. Exits 0 on pass, non-zero on fail
#   2. Is referenced by a stamp under tests/stamps/
#   3. Lives self-contained (no shared state with other tests)
#
# Example stamp pointing here:
#
#   ---
#   name: api-health-check
#   kind: test
#   test_kind: integration
#   language: bash
#   location: tests/scripts/api-health-check.sh
#   run_command: tests/scripts/api-health-check.sh
#   ---
#
# See test-rules.md for the full stamp model.
